lead_paragraph: Kalani Brown scored 17 points and Kristy Wallace added 15 to help No. 4 Baylor defeat Texas Tech 82-51 in a Big 12 quarterfinal on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: No. 4 Baylor Women Roll Past Texas Tech 82-51
